<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="recall-vt">recall <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'kɔːl/    美 /rɪ'kɔːl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>回忆；回想：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s time to recall those beautiful days we spent together. 
现在该回忆一下我们共同度过的那些美好日子。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>召回；收回：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>More than 3,000 cars were recalled yesterday because of a brake problem. 
昨天3000多辆汽车因为刹车问题被召回。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Legend has it that the origin of the Dragon Boat Festival is to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (召回) the soul of Qu Yuan.  （2014 江苏改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. recall  </p></div>